<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 850px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #dc2626;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #dc2626;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .doc-subtitle {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .filing-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            background: #fee2e2;
            color: #991b1b;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .entity-section {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .entity-name {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .entity-detail {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .entity-detail strong {
            color: #111827;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .filing-meta {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .meta-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
        }

        .meta-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .meta-value {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .section-title::before {
            content: '';
            width: 4px;
            height: 20px;
            background: #dc2626;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .section-content {
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .filing-details-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .detail-card {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
        }

        .detail-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .detail-value {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .compliance-box {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .compliance-box-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .compliance-box-content {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #1e40af;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .document-list {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .document-list-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .document-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #e5e7eb;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        .document-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .document-item::before {
            content: '✓';
            display: inline-block;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: #d1fae5;
            color: #065f46;
            border-radius: 50%;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 20px;
            margin-right: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .status-badge.submitted {
            background: #d1fae5;
            color: #065f46;
        }

        .status-badge.pending {
            background: #fef3c7;
            color: #92400e;
        }

        .status-badge.approved {
            background: #dbeafe;
            color: #1e40af;
        }

        .declaration-section {
            background: #fef3c7;
            border: 2px solid #fbbf24;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .declaration-title {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .declaration-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #78350f;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 48px;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .signature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 32px;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }

        .signature-block {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .signature-line {
            border-top: 2px solid #111827;
            padding-top: 8px;
            margin-top: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .signature-title {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 48px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            text-align: center;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        .footer-note {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        @media print {
            body {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .filing-meta {
                break-inside: avoid;
            }

            .declaration-section {
                break-inside: avoid;
            }

            .signature-section {
                break-inside: avoid;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="doc-title">Regulatory Filing</div>
        <div class="doc-subtitle">{{#if filingType}}{{filingType}}{{else}}Official Regulatory Submission{{/if}}</div>
        <div class="filing-badge">{{#if regulatoryBody}}{{regulatoryBody}}{{else}}Compliance Filing{{/if}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="entity-section">
        <div class="entity-name">{{companyName}}</div>
        {{#if companyAddress}}<div class="entity-detail">{{{companyAddress}}}</div>{{/if}}
        {{#if registrationNumber}}<div class="entity-detail"><strong>Registration Number:</strong> {{registrationNumber}}</div>{{/if}}
    </div>

    <div class="filing-meta">
        <div class="meta-card">
            <div class="meta-label">Filing Reference</div>
            <div class="meta-value">{{#if filingNumber}}{{filingNumber}}{{else}}FIL-{{generatedDate}}{{/if}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-card">
            <div class="meta-label">Filing Date</div>
            <div class="meta-value">{{#if filingDate}}{{filingDate}}{{else}}{{generatedDate}}{{/if}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-card">
            <div class="meta-label">Status</div>
            <div class="meta-value">
                <span class="status-badge {{#if filingStatus}}{{filingStatus}}{{else}}submitted{{/if}}">
                    {{#if filingStatus}}{{filingStatus}}{{else}}Submitted{{/if}}
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {{#if filingPurpose}}
    <div class="section-title">Purpose of Filing</div>
    <div class="section-content">
        <p>{{filingPurpose}}</p>
    </div>
    {{/if}}

    <div class="section-title">Filing Details</div>
    <div class="filing-details-grid">
        {{#if filingType}}
        <div class="detail-card">
            <div class="detail-label">Filing Type</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{filingType}}</div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if filingPeriod}}
        <div class="detail-card">
            <div class="detail-label">Period Covered</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{filingPeriod}}</div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if regulatoryBody}}
        <div class="detail-card">
            <div class="detail-label">Regulatory Authority</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{regulatoryBody}}</div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if deadlineDate}}
        <div class="detail-card">
            <div class="detail-label">Due Date</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{deadlineDate}}</div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
    </div>

    {{#if filingDetails}}
    <div class="section-title">Filing Summary</div>
    <div class="section-content">
        {{{filingDetails}}}
    </div>
    {{/if}}

    {{#if sections}}
    {{#each sections}}
    <div class="section-title">{{this.heading}}</div>
    <div class="section-content">
        {{{this.content}}}
    </div>
    {{/each}}
    {{/if}}

    {{#if attachedDocuments}}
    <div class="section-title">Attached Documents</div>
    <div class="document-list">
        <div class="document-list-title">Supporting Documentation</div>
        {{#each attachedDocuments}}
        <div class="document-item">{{this}}</div>
        {{/each}}
    </div>
    {{/if}}

    <div class="compliance-box">
        <div class="compliance-box-title">⚠️ Compliance Notice</div>
        <div class="compliance-box-content">
            {{#if complianceNotice}}
            {{complianceNotice}}
            {{else}}
            This filing is submitted in accordance with the applicable regulations and statutory requirements. All information provided is true, accurate, and complete to the best of our knowledge. The organization undertakes to comply with all regulatory obligations and to maintain proper records as required by law.
            {{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="declaration-section">
        <div class="declaration-title">Declaration</div>
        <div class="declaration-text">
            {{#if declarationText}}
            {{declarationText}}
            {{else}}
            I/We hereby declare that the information provided in this regulatory filing is true, complete, and accurate. I/We understand that any false statement or misrepresentation may result in legal penalties and regulatory action. I/We accept full responsibility for the accuracy of this submission and undertake to notify the regulatory authority of any material changes.
            {{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="signature-grid">
            <div class="signature-block">
                <div class="signature-line">{{#if authorizedSignatory}}{{authorizedSignatory}}{{else}}Authorized Signatory{{/if}}</div>
                <div class="signature-title">{{#if signatoryTitle}}{{signatoryTitle}}{{else}}Designated Officer{{/if}}</div>
                <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 8px;">Date: {{#if signatureDate}}{{signatureDate}}{{else}}{{generatedDate}}{{/if}}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="signature-block">
                <div class="signature-line">{{companyName}}</div>
                <div class="signature-title">Company Seal/Stamp</div>
                <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 8px;">Place: {{#if filingPlace}}{{filingPlace}}{{else}}[Location]{{/if}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <div class="footer-note">
            This is an official regulatory filing document.
        </div>
        <div class="footer-note">
            Filing Reference: {{#if filingNumber}}{{filingNumber}}{{else}}FIL-{{generatedDate}}{{/if}} | Generated on {{generatedDate}}
        </div>
        {{#if footerText}}
        <div class="footer-note" style="margin-top: 12px;">
            {{footerText}}
        </div>
        {{else}}
        <div class="footer-note" style="margin-top: 12px;">
            Generated with MM Docs AI • Professional Workspace
        </div>
        {{/if}}
    </div>
</body>

</html>
